<script>
function popup(tag, url)
{
var dataUrl = tag.attr('data-url');
var dataTitle = tag.attr('data-title');

if (! dataUrl || ! dataTitle) {
return;
}

url = url.replace(/:url/g, dataUrl)
.replace(/:title/g, dataTitle)
.replace(/:encodeTitle/g, encodeURIComponent(dataTitle));

popupWin = window.open(url, 'Поделиться', 'location,width=800,height=600,top=0');
popupWin.focus();
return false;
}

function ajaxPopup(tag) {
$.fancybox.open('https://rosstat.gov.ru/sharing/email', {
type: "ajax",
scrolling: "no",
padding: "0",
fitToView: true,
autoWidth: true,
autoHeight: true,
ajax: {
type: "get",
data: {key: tag.attr('data-key'), type: tag.attr('data-type')}
},
helpers: {
overlay: {
css: {
background: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)'
}
}
}
});
}

function mail(tag, url)
{
var dataUrl = tag.attr('data-url');
var dataTitle = tag.attr('data-title');

if (! dataUrl || ! dataTitle) {
return;
}

url = url.replace(/:url/g, dataUrl)
.replace(/:title/g, dataTitle)
.replace(/:encodeTitle/g, encodeURIComponent(dataTitle));

window.location.href = url;
return false;
}
</script>

<script>
$('.list__btn-add a').click(function (e) {
e.preventDefault();

var link = $(this);
var page = link.data('page');
if (! page) {
page = 2;
}

$.ajax({
method: 'get',
url: link.data('href'),
data: {page: page},
success: function(data) {
var linkParent = link.parent();
var parentBlock = linkParent.parent();

parentBlock.children('.list__items').first().append(data.view);

if (! data.more) {
linkParent.hide();
}

page++;
link.data('page', page);
}
});
});
</script>
<script>
$(function () {
function updateCaptchaAudio(elements = null) {
let subjects = elements !== null ? $(elements)
: $('.captcha-audio').filter('[src]');

subjects.attr('src', 'https://rosstat.gov.ru/audiocaptcha/audio?we5qxIrI' + Math.random());
}

$('.captcha__link-refresh').on('click', function (event) {
event.preventDefault();
event.stopImmediatePropagation();

$('.captcha-img').attr('src', 'https://rosstat.gov.ru/audiocaptcha/ru?9UclUD5F' + Math.random());
});

$('.captcha-img').first().on('load', function (event) {
event.stopImmediatePropagation();

if ($('.captcha-audio').is('[src]')) {
updateCaptchaAudio();
}
});

$('.captcha__link-audio').on('click', function (event) {
event.preventDefault();
event.stopImmediatePropagation();

let audio = this.querySelector('audio');

if (!audio.hasAttribute('src')) {
updateCaptchaAudio(audio);
}

if (audio.paused) {
audio.play();
}
else {
audio.pause();
audio.currentTime = 0;
}
});
});
</script>
<script>
$('.misprint__form form').on('submit', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();

let form = $(this);

$.ajax({
method: form.attr('method'),
url: form.attr('action'),
data: form.serialize(),
success: function () {
$.fancybox.close();
},
error: function (data) {
let errors = data.responseJSON.errors;

$.each(errors, function (key, value) {
let element = form.find('[name="'+key+'"]');
let parent = element.parents('.form-group');
element.addClass('is-invalid');
parent.find('.invalid-feedback').text(value);
});

$('.captcha__link-refresh').click();
$('[name="captcha"]').val('');
},
});
})
</script>
